  "description": "Use this skill to define, document, and validate KPI metrics for CRM Analytics \u2014 covering metric formula design, dimension selection, target-dataset modeling, benchmark setting, and the KPI register that must exist before any dashboard or lens is built. Trigger keywords: KPI definition CRM Analytics, analytics metric design, analytics target attainment, CRM Analytics measures vs dimensions, analytics benchmark. NOT for building CRM Analytics dashboards or lenses (use analytics/dashboard-design), SOQL report KPI design, or Marketing Cloud analytics KPI work.",
  "file_location": "skills/admin/analytics-kpi-definition",
  "id": "admin/analytics-kpi-definition",
  "inputs": [
    "List of KPIs stakeholders need to track",
    "Business definitions for each metric (what counts, what excludes)",
    "Target values or benchmark sources",
    "CRM Analytics dataset name and available fields"
  ],
  "name": "analytics-kpi-definition",
  "official_sources": [
    "Calculate Key Performance Indicators Using CRM Analytics \u2014 https://help.salesforce.com/s/articleView?id=sf.bi_kpis.htm",
